THat when your Petitioners firſt ſaw that Act of Parliament made in Anno 1651 . Intituled An Act for increaſe of Shipping; and incouragement of the Navigation of this Nation, They had 
   •
opes that their then languiſhing condition ſhould have bin thereby reſtored; But having found by continued ſad experience, that notwithſtanding the good intendments ot that Act, The Navigation, and Trading Ships of this Nation, and conſequently the imployment of your Petitioners have dayly declined, and are now almoſt quite extinct;
